  "markup": "\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003EWant to make an easy \u003Cstrong\u003E$1,000\u003C/strong\u003E? Refer a qualified friend or colleague under this program!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003EWe believe good people, know more good people, and we want to hire them!\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-spacerun: yes;\u0022\u003E\u0026nbsp; \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E"
